OL,3,CPolitician believes home was targeted
OL,4,Cafter vehicle tyres slashed
OL,6,FA senior Guernsey politician says his
OL,7,Fhome has been targeted by vandals
OL,8,Fafter the tyres on his motorbike,
OL,9,Felectric bike and his grandson's car
OL,10,Fwere slashed.
OL,12,FDeputy Peter Roffey, who is standing
OL,13,Fdown following this month's election,
OL,14,Fdiscovered the damage when returning
OL,15,Fto the island on Friday following a
OL,16,Ffamily bereavement.
