OL,3,CPolitician believes home was targeted
OL,4,Cafter vehicle tyres slashed
OL,6,FThe Employment and Social Security
OL,7,FCommittee President explains he does
OL,8,Fnot know who carried out the acts, but
OL,9,Fbelieves they are politically
OL,10,Fmotivated and is urging those involved
OL,11,Fto talk to him about their issues.
OL,13,FDeputy Roffey adds: "I'm fairly sure
OL,14,Fit is somebody that I've upset, and if
OL,15,FI've upset someone at all then I'm
OL,16,Fsorry, but come and talk about it.
OL,18,F"Let's discuss things because
OL,19,Fpoliticians do have to make difficult
OL,20,Fdecisions and they will upset people
OL,21,Ffrom time to time."
