OL,6,FHe goes on to say: "If you feel like
OL,7,Fthe States are doing something wrong,
OL,8,For I'm doing something wrong within
OL,9,Fthe States or one of my committees,
OL,10,Ftalk to me, try and persuade me,
OL,11,Fbecause that's the only way you're
OL,12,Factually going to change the course of
OL,13,Fevents.
OL,15,F"None of my colleagues, and certainly
OL,16,Fnot myself, are going to make a
OL,17,Fdifferent decision just because of a
OL,18,Fthreat of vandalism."
