OL,3,CPolitician believes home was targeted
OL,4,Cafter vehicle tyres slashed
OL,6,FWriting on social media, Deputy Roffey
OL,7,Fadds: "And people wonder why many
OL,8,Fislanders are deterred from standing
OL,9,Ffor the States.
OL,11,F"All slightly sad. Not the worst I've
OL,12,Freceived by any means but still leaves
OL,13,Fan unpleasant taste in the mouth."
OL,15,FDeputy Roffey has now had his
OL,16,Fmotorbike repaired and the vandalism
OL,17,Fis being investigated by Guernsey
OL,18,FPolice.
